<p>
  All costs are based on the information we receive prior to this quote being
  given. Costs will be charged in addition to these estimates for time incurred
  for extra content and/or changes in direction from either the original contact
  or new decision makers which contradict the initial brief. Our hourly rate is
  £65 per hour for work outside of these estimates. Our processes are
  <strong class="accent">efficient</strong> and <strong class="accent">effective</strong>, we will work with
  you in such a manner that revisions are dealt with in the most efficient way
  <strong class="accent">keeping within timescales and budgets</strong>. We are proactive with our requests and
  will work with you and your contributing departments enabling us to keep to
  the agreed budget and time scales.
</p>

<p>
  All jobs up to £500 will be invoiced on receiving the go ahead/purchase order
  number.

  For payments over £500 a 50% invoice will be issued on receiving the go
  ahead/purchase order number with the other 50% to be invoiced after 30 days.
</p>

